\f1\b0\fs40 \cf0 {\listtext	\'95	}24 (1/4-inch-thick) diagonal slices cut from a long thin loaf Italian or {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://www.foodterms.com/encyclopedia/french-bread/index.html"}}{\fldrslt \cf2 French bread}}\
{\listtext	\'95	}1/2 cup plus 2 tablespoons olive oil\
