{\listtext	\'95	}3/4 teaspoon freshly ground black pepper\
{\listtext	\'95	}4 cups thinly sliced red onions\
{\listtext	\'95	}4 tablespoons balsamic vinegar\
{\listtext	\'95	}1/2 cup soft {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://www.foodterms.com/encyclopedia/cheese/index.html"}}{\fldrslt \cf2 cheese}}, such as blue or {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://www.foodterms.com/encyclopedia/goat/index.html"}}{\fldrslt \cf2 goat}}\
